      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p><style>[data-colorid=adluh61akq]{color:#4269b8} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=adluh61akq]{color:#476ebd}[data-colorid=ay62tqbdu2]{color:#4269b8} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ay62tqbdu2]{color:#476ebd}[data-colorid=uiws3oncf6]{color:#4269b8} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=uiws3oncf6]{color:#476ebd}[data-colorid=dm1egoh12n]{color:#4269b8} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=dm1egoh12n]{color:#476ebd}[data-colorid=l8g9vsjlm1]{color:#4269b8} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=l8g9vsjlm1]{color:#476ebd}</style>To add render time Subdivisions to your geometry in Solaris are handled via the <strong><span data-colorid=\"adluh61akq\">MeshEdit</span></strong> node.<br /><br />Create and connect a <strong><span data-colorid=\"dm1egoh12n\">MeshEdit</span></strong> node to your Solaris graph.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640652/RenderMan_Solaris_AddSub_MeshEdit2.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433079057&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=258\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640652/RenderMan_Solaris_AddSub_MeshEdit2.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433079057&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"286\" data-width=\"997\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640676\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_AddSub_MeshEdit2.gif\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/gif\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640652\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"3f234a3e-da1b-4e3b-b9dc-ec743d9ccd46\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640652/RenderMan_Solaris_AddSub_MeshEdit2.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433079057&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=997&amp;height=286 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640652/RenderMan_Solaris_AddSub_MeshEdit2.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433079057&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=258 1x\" /></span><p /><p>Select the Primitive(s) to be subdivided and then <strong><span data-colorid=\"l8g9vsjlm1\">Set / Create </span></strong>a Subdivision Scheme and select <strong><span data-colorid=\"ay62tqbdu2\">Catmull Clark</span></strong></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640652/RenderMan_Solaris_AddSub.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433078813&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=543\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640652/RenderMan_Solaris_AddSub.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433078813&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"602\" data-width=\"997\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640670\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_AddSub.gif\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/gif\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640652\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"e2b29d73-57ea-4eb2-91e0-76ec7cf14d9c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640652/RenderMan_Solaris_AddSub.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433078813&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=997&amp;height=602 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640652/RenderMan_Solaris_AddSub.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433078813&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=543 1x\" /></span><p /><hr /><p><br /><strong><span data-colorid=\"uiws3oncf6\">Example</span></strong>&nbsp;<br />Before Subdivision :</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640652/RenderManStudio_Solaris_Without_SubD.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433078813&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=506\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640652/RenderManStudio_Solaris_Without_SubD.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433078813&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"720\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640667\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManStudio_Solaris_Without_SubD.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640652\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"b086b52f-5e5d-4712-9b16-cee114c51847\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640652/RenderManStudio_Solaris_Without_SubD.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433078813&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1800&amp;height=1012 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640652/RenderManStudio_Solaris_Without_SubD.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433078813&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=506 1x\" /></span><p><br />And, after Subdivision :</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640652/RenderManStudio_Solaris_WithSubD.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433078812&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=506\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640652/RenderManStudio_Solaris_WithSubD.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433078812&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"720\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640664\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManStudio_Solaris_WithSubD.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640652\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"d1d503c5-2139-4f64-9ac2-b543a72a7cbf\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640652/RenderManStudio_Solaris_WithSubD.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433078812&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1800&amp;height=1012 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640652/RenderManStudio_Solaris_WithSubD.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433078812&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=506 1x\" /></span><hr /><p />"
